<div class='player-hero__poster' id='player-hero-poster'>
<img class='player-hero__image player-hero__image--4x3' src='http://img.tedcdn.com/r/images.ted.com/images/ted/a8d46be076dd754d8c9b40fc4b8ab3bebbef56ef_1600x1200.jpg?ll=1&amp;quality=89&amp;w=800'>
